Detailed Description

template<typename COORDINATE>
class BW::Range1DT< COORDINATE >

This class is used to represent a 1 dimensional range.

template<typename COORDINATE>
bool BW::Range1DT< COORDINATE >::contains ( const Range1DT< COORDINATE > &  range  )  const [inline]

This determines whether one range is inside another.

Parameters:
range The range to test.
Returns:
True if the range lies within this range, false if it has values outside of this range. The endpoints are considered to be inside the range.

This gets the i'th coordinate of the range.

Parameters:
i The index of the coordinate to get.
Returns:
